<year box="[950,1013,674,700]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">2007</year>
</number>
a
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<journalOrPublisher jopScore="0.35777694" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">The Holarctic Region was probably the ancestral area of this genus, and the Neotropical and Oriental occurrences are due to subsequent expansion of distribution range followed by local speciations</journalOrPublisher>
